## 5. Direct Transport (`apps/client/src/layers/shared/lib/direct-transport.ts`)

The direct transport delegates to `marketplaceStubs.listInstalledPackages`, which comes from `createMarketplaceMethods`. Since we updated that in step 3, the direct transport's assignment `listInstalledPackages = marketplaceStubs.listInstalledPackages` will pick up the new signature automatically. Verify it compiles.

